<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ʿny qḍy̱ rby ạlḥnwn wdẖạq gẖṣạt ạlmnwn mḥrrạaⁿ ạ̉sry ạlsjwn rb ạlwry fạdy ạlạ̉nạm ạlqrạr- jỷt sẖfạaⁿʾ mt fdạʾ fyạ lḥbk ạlʿjyb lys swạk ffy dmạk njwt mn mwt rhyb fkyf ạ̉nsy̱ sẖạfy jrwḥy mạḥy ậtẖạmy fkyf ạ̉nsy̱ lwlạk ạ̉nt ḥby wʿwny rby ạ̉nt fy ạlḥsẖạ fln ạ̉nsạk 2- kyf qḍy̱ yạ llʿjb fwq ṣlyb mn kẖsẖb bạlṣlb qd mḥy̱ ạlgẖḍb wsyṭ ṣlḥ wslạm 3- sạlt ynạbyʿ dmạh ḥbạaⁿ ḥnạnạaⁿ llkẖṭạẗ mạ mn rjạʾ bswạh ywly ạlkẖlạṣ bạltmạm</lyrics>
<title>ʿny qḍy̱</title>
